quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  77,41,Naye mazima abatya Katonda bagenda kubeera mu bisiikirize n'emigga egikulukuta
  77,42,N'ebibala byebaliba bagala
  77,43,Nga bagambibwa nti mulye era munywe nga mweyagala
  77,44,Mazima ffe bwetutyo bwetusasula abakozi b'obulungi
  77,45,Ku lunaku olwo okubonaabona kugenda kubeera kwabo abalulimbisa
  77,46,"(Kuno ku nsi abakafiiri bagambwa nti) mulye, era mweyagale kitono, wabula mumanye nti muli bonoonyi (naye mukimanye nti waliyo enkomerero)"
  77,47,Ku lunaku olwo okubonaabona kugenda kubeera kwabo abalulimbisa
  77,48,Bwebalagirwa okusaala tebasaala
  77,49,Ku lunaku olwo okubonaabona kugenda kubeera kwabo abalulimbisa
  77,50,Olwo bigamboki ebitali Kur'ani byebagenda okukkiriza